Prime Minister Harper Says Federal Election Will Take Place on May 2

-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 
2011-03-26T13:22:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-26/prime-minister-harper-says-federal-election-will-take-place-on-may-2.html
Canadian Prime Minister Stephen
Harper said a federal election will take place on May 2.  Harper made the comments today in Ottawa, after his
government was brought down by opposition parties yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Theophilos Argitis in Ottawa at 
